text.paragraph:
RESTASIS MULTIDOSE is contraindicated in patients with known or suspected hypersensitivity to any of the ingredients in the formulation [ see
Adverse Reactions (6.2)
].

list.item:
Potential for Eye Injury and Contamination [ see
Warnings and Precautions (5.1)
]

text.paragraph:
Advise patients to not allow the tip of the bottle to touch the eye or any surface, as this may contaminate the emulsion. Advise patients to not touch the bottle tip to their eye to avoid the potential for injury to the eye [see 

                        Warnings and Precautions (5.1)
                     ].
